('96023','33124','5','Elegant villa with 2 apartments in Santa Ponsa for sale'),
('96024','33125','5','The villa stands on a 1.138m² large flat plot in a quiet residential area in Nova Santa Ponsa. Just a short drive away from several golf courses, marinas with trendy restaurants.  this villa was built 2002 with quality materials and offers 2 residential floors each with one apartment. The ground floor offers 194m² of living space, a living room with open built in kitchen, 2 large bedrooms each with a bathroom en suite, guest toilet and covered terraces. On the 1st floor are located in a 122m² livingspace a salon-dining room, 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a guest toilet and a 18m² large balcony. In the basement it has a multi function-room with a skylight window perfect for a cinema room, fitness area or spa. Features include air conditioning h/c, aluminum double glazed windows, aluminum shutters, 2 fitted kitchens and furniture. Outside boasts a beautifully landscaped and automatically irrigated mediterranean garden with a large pool 5x10m. A garage and 3 parking spaces are also available'),
